Package org.neo4j.io.os

Class OsBeanUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.io.os.OsBeanUtil
  • public final class OsBeanUtil
extends Object
    Utility class that exposes methods from proprietary implementations of OperatingSystemMXBean. Able to work on Oracle JDK and IBM JDK. Methods never fail but instead return VALUE_UNAVAILABLE if such method is not exposed by the underlying MX bean.
